# AI Knowledge Assistant — Concept

## Overview

The AI Knowledge Assistant is designed to help users quickly find answers to common questions by retrieving and summarizing relevant documentation.

Instead of navigating multiple help articles, users can ask questions in natural language and receive clear, structured responses based on existing documentation.

## Purpose

The goal of this assistant is to:

  * reduce time spent searching for information
  * improve user self-service
  * provide consistent, accurate answers
  * reduce repetitive support tickets

## Example Use Cases

Users might ask:

  * “Why isn’t my dashboard loading?”
  * “How do I export my data?”
  * “Why is my integration not working?”

The assistant responds with:

  * relevant steps
  * troubleshooting guidance
  * links to full documentation (if needed)
